0-0000-000000000005}">UINT</BaseType><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[Invalid]]></Text><Enum>0</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates no or invalid information, e.g. no connection or component not yet ready.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[FreeMovement]]></Text><Enum>101</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates a freely moving PlanarMover.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[OnTrack]]></Text><Enum>102</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates that the PlanarMover is moving on a PlanarTrack.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[JoiningTrack]]></Text><Enum>103</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates that the PlanarMover is approaching a PlanarTrack to join it.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[LeavingTrack]]></Text><Enum>104</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates that the PlanarMover is leaving a PlanarTrack to move freely afterwards.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[ExternalSetpointGeneration]]></Text><Enum>105</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates that the PlanarMover is following externally provided setpoints.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[CRotationFreeMovement]]></Text><Enum>106</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates that the PlanarMover is only rotating the C coordinate in free movement, X and Y are standing.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[CRotationOnTrack]]></Text><Enum>107</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates that the PlanarMover is only rotating the C coordinate on a track, X and Y are standing.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><EnumInfo><Text><![CDATA[ExternalBodeplot]]></Text><Enum>109</Enum><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates that the PlanarMover is following external bodeplot setpoints.]]></Comment></EnumInfo><Properties><Property><Name>plcAttribute_qualified_only</Name></Property><Property><Name>plcAttribute_to_string</Name></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name GUID="{1724CCE2-4FE1-4A80-AEC5-6F25F9789895}" Namespace="MC">MoverBusy</Name><Comment><![CDATA[Indicates the busy state of the PlanarMover.]]></Commen